Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years have passed since the \NWar of the Best in Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew each \Ncompleted individual training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on their way to the \Nnext stage - the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they reached the Fish-Man Island \Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:35.86,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Ryugu Palace in Shock!\N The Kidnapping of Shirahoshi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:41.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}SOUTHEAST OF THE FISH-MAN ISLAND\NIN THE DEEP SEA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:45.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all the way to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tom-san told me that one of his family\N members at home is also a shipwright, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it must've been difficult \Nto come to the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trained by Tom-san since I was a kid\N and I came here with a ship that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were my brother's pupil,\N I bet it's quite a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's called the Thousand \NSunny and it's my masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after we entered the Fish-Man Island,\N it was taken away by the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of reason that I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could give \Nme a clue as to Sunny's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a ship sinks in these parts, \Nit usually gets carried by the tide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ends up at a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the Sunny will be there too.\N Count on me, completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get there soon. \NThe place known as the Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait, Megalo! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama, Brother-sama,\N everybody at the palace, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going out without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be home by dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for a "walk"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on, Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he left the doors open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if something happens to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, hurry up! \NSee if the Princess is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're riding my bones too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here! \NPrincess Shirahoshi is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Mermaid Princess is not here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! This is a matter of \Ngreat consequence to the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did this happen?! Who did this?!\N She must have been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate that connects the Fish-Man\N Island and the Ryugu Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the switch to open it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, hurry and go back to Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell him what is going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to do as we're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told us the only way \Nwe'll live is if we obey them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are "they"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna kill us if you don't tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:07:04.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A FEW HOURS AGO THE FISH-MAN DISTRICT "NOAH"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are such lowly creatures - \Nthey can't even breathe in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you pirates under \Nthe control of Hordy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should all be happy! Because you \Ncan be part of this historic mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Vander Decken \Nof the Flying Dutchman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of the cursed ghost ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm his descendant.\N I'm not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I am cursed as well. I can't \Nswim even though I'm a Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this devil power alongside\N of the Mark-Mark curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you human right there! Step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys serious? Don't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Hachi-san!\N--Hatchan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Hachi-san!\N--It's Hatchan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Energy Steroids will\N do nothing but ruin you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of destroying the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the\N Great Knight Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi-san, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your voice anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were an officer \Nof the pirate group that I admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a coward. \NIt's time for a generation change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To teach humans a lesson, \Nwe need the Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Neptune is in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all taught us that \Nwe're the supreme race!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Arlong-san lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken! Hyouzou! Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even refused \NArlong-san's offer back then
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why are you helping these youths now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping? I'm just in this for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong was stingy so he couldn't pay me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt sorry for him that he could only \Ntake crappy swordsmen like you with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi from the Arlong Pirates?\N Oh, sweet memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your captain even tried to make\N me work under him at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was ridiculous! \NI won't work under anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san had a dream and an ability\N to take action that I could respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, he was too \Nrough and lacked cleverness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you guys were running wild on the sea,\N we were all too young to become pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all witnessed what they did \Nso we plan things more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we've learned from \Nour predecessors' failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue where Arlong left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the group I admired so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your opposition is so\Ndiscouraging, Hachi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy who shattered \NArlong's dream is here, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't mind at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called me his friend even though I'm \Na former member of the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you are my friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Straw Hat Luffy saved my life.\N I wish I could go see him now but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too ashamed to face him when somebody\N is trying to keep Arlong's dream alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic of you to \Nbecome friends with a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disgusted by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock on to you, Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot how pirates do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is something to say,\N you have to use violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he throwing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I touched you just now,\N you became my mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I throw or where I \Nthrow it, it's like a living bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will strike you at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The knife he just threw somewhere else...\N --...Flew at the octopus Fish-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark-Mark curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there are a number \Nof ways to defend yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... You have so many arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew about your power - I heard the rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hordy, he's trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he told you, Hachi-san. \NVander Decken is not working under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are allies on equal footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're annoying me anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they will chase you, chase you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chase you and chase you \Nto the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get out of here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, now I can get away! \NIn the water, arrows will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They aren't even slowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have two marks - one for each palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't washed my right hand for 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I touched Princess \NShirahoshi and designated her as my mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand? It doesn't matter \Nif it's love or a weapon that I throw,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll both follow \Nuntil the furthest hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he could continue\N stalking her insidiously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without showing himself or \Ngetting caught by Neptune's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sinister guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sinister! Sinister! Sinister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you human pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've seen Decken's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the first stage of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the Ryugu Palace\N is impregnable but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...someone has been able to pierce\N the defenses for 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's him - Vander Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for this mission,\N you'll be thrown by Decken
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fly to the Mermaid \NPrincess in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you'll be landing is the \Nsolid wall of the tower though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, open the gate from inside the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let us in - that is your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way! If we get thrown...\N--...We could die from hitting the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you humans to do it \Nbecause your lives aren't so important!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humans are less \Nvaluable than slaves here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who survive hitting\N the wall carry out your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you succeed it, I'll set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse to do it, I'll kick \Nyou out of the bubble right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way... If we leave the bubble,\N we'll drown for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you have no choice but wager \Non the possibility you'll survive, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a new history for \Nthe Fish-Men will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we conquer the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to you soon, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:58.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}THE NORTHWEST SIDE OF THE RYUGU PALACE\NA PASSAGEWAY TO THE HARD SHELL TOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:02.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Skeleton, get to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... We have to open the gate or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hordy will kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have a question for you guys. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, you have to stay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, at that place called \Nthe Ryugu Palace... Is she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She is there! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go. Even if it kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going?! You never learn!\N If she's beautiful, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she's beautiful, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met her but I \Nheard she's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's beautiful, just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, I'll go, at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now lead me to the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:18:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong with him?\N--I don't know but we have to take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be handcuffed if \Nyou're going to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want as long as \NI can see the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cook for the Mermaid \NPrincess if you handcuff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were gonna resist! Cart them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards wanna ruin my chance \Nto get close to the Mermaid Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?! Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, you beat all the soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do anything wrong but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their fault - they tried to handcuff me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're part of the Straw Hats...\N--Dangerous people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:19:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, everybody's looking at us coldly \Nlike they're a bunch of deep-sea fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining! What's done is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think before you act!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You beat the half of them with kung fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to compliment me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the voice of a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a man covered \Nwith blood at the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy from the Fish-Man District!\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I am a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hachi! It's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hurt?! What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... It's you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you... Is Straw Hat with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here! Wait for a moment!\N I'll treat you in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon all your friends... Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't wanna get involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with this island! Get out of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New Fish-Man Pirates will \Ncome and attack the island soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Ryugu Kingdom will... fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a kidnapping!\N Somebody kidnapped the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And pirates are falling like \Nrain at the tower! In any event,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're your enemies! They're attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapped?! Shirahoshi?! Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's making a \Nraid now? What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?! \NWe're occupying the palace ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Don't answer"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for us to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...We have to open the gate at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come out of Shark now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'd rather stay in here still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it out here after 10 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is racing! This is very bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can it be bad? You \Njust got out of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what they call an adventure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your heart is racing, that's an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say "the Sea Forest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? Something fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a grave that I haven't\N been to since they built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the place that I've wanted\N to go to the most for 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:34.74,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}THE SEA FOREST IN THE DEEP SEA
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 10 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since her assassination in broad daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which threw the Fish-Man\N Island in an uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princes have grown into tough soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi is still in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody forgets your ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy's plans for revenge are underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates he has sent lay \Nsiege to the Ryugu Palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and throw it into a state of panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew has been caught up in the attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the once impregnable Ryugu \NPalace gate is breached,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New Fish-Man Pirates have arrived, \Nintent on destroying the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hordy's Onslaught! The Retaliatory \NPlan Set Into Motion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
